text: R0 or R00 may refer to: * Haplogroup R0, a gene * R0, the Brussels Ring-road * R0, basic reproduction number, an important concept in epidemiology * R0, net reproduction rate, an important concept in population ecology and demography * R0, the distance from the Sun to the galactic center in astronomy * .r00, a software file extension * R00, abnormalities of heart beat ICD-10 code * Samsung YP-R0, a digital audio player ==See also== * RO (disambiguation)
